        "action": "Require companies to issue refunds within 48 hours",
        "additional_details": "It is unfair that businesses can hold client money for long periods of time, which they owe to the client. This is to the detriment of the consumer and much to the advantage of the business.",
        "background": "The Government should set a legal time limit of 48 hours for companies to issue a refund.",
